org.matsim.core.utils.io

Class MatsimXmlParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.xml.sax.helpers.DefaultHandler
      • org.matsim.core.utils.io.MatsimXmlParser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MatsimReader, ContentHandler, DTDHandler, EntityResolver, ErrorHandler
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ConfigReader, CountsReaderMatsimV1, EventsConverterXML, EventsReaderXMLv1, FacilitiesReaderMatsimV1, HouseholdsReaderV10, HouseholdsStreamingReaderV10, MatricesReaderMatsimV1, MatsimCountsReader, MatsimFacilitiesReader, MatsimMatricesReader, MatsimNetworkReader, NetworkChangeEventsParser, NetworkReaderMatsimV1, NetworkReaderMatsimV2, ObjectAttributesXmlReader, PopulationReader, TransitScheduleReaderV1, TransitScheduleReaderV2, VehicleReaderV1

    public abstract class MatsimXmlParser
extends org.xml.sax.helpers.DefaultHandler
implements MatsimReader
    An abstract XML-Parser which can be easily extended for reading custom XML-formats. This class handles all the low level functionality required to parse xml-files. Extending classes have only to implement startTag(java.lang.String, org.xml.sax.Attributes, java.util.Stack<java.lang.String>) and endTag(java.lang.String, java.lang.String, java.util.Stack<java.lang.String>) to implement a custom parser.
    The parser implements a custom EntityResolver to look for DTDs in the MATSim world.

    Notes:
    • If implementing classes want to override the final methods, the will have to resort to delegation.
    Author:
    mrieser

      • readFile

        public final void readFile(String filename)
                    throws UncheckedIOException
        Parses the specified file. The file can be gzip-compressed and is decompressed on-the-fly while parsing. A gzip-compressed file must have the ending ".gz" to be correctly recognized. The passed filename may or may not contain the ending ".gz". If no uncompressed file is found with the specified name, the ending ".gz" will be added to the filename and a compressed file will be searched for and read if found.
        Specified by:
        readFile in interface MatsimReader
        Parameters:
        filename - The filename of the file to read, optionally ending with ".gz" to force reading a gzip-compressed file.
        Throws:
        UncheckedIOException
